i)Count the no of ways
ii)Min
iii)Max

Do find all possbile ways->Recursion->DP


Shortcut (TOP DOWN):
1)Try to represent the problem in terms of index
2)Do all possible stuff on that index according to the problem statement
3)count all way->Sum up all stuffs
4)find min->min of all stuffs
5)find max->max of all stuffs


BOTTOM UP :

1)copy the base cases
2) Change the indexes in the opposite direction
3)Copy the recurrence
